dc_description_s: Honduras Household Cable TV Service Census Data, 2013 is a polygon theme representing Manzanas (6th level administrative units) in Honduras as of 2013. This map is georeferenced to the surface of the earth and fit to World Geodetic System (1984) coordinates. Attribute data include summary results of the 2013 Hondurasian census questions regarding whether the household has cable TV service. The documentation of these variables can be found in the "H08_CABLE" section from the accompanying code book. This dataset is part of Honduras 2013 Census collection.
dc_title_s: Honduras Household Cable TV Service Census Data, 2013
